## Bytes ↔ Integer

### Bytes → Integer

```python
int.from_bytes(b"\x01\x02", "big")
# 258
```

```python
int.from_bytes(b"\x01\x02", "little")
# 513
```

### Integer → Bytes

```python
(258).to_bytes(2, "big")
# b'\x01\x02'
```

