## Endianness

### Little Endian

```python
b"\x78\x56\x34\x12"
```

represents

```text
0x12345678
```

Python:

```python
int.from_bytes(b"\x78\x56\x34\x12", "little")
```

### Big Endian

```python
int.from_bytes(b"\x12\x34\x56\x78", "big")
```

