## XOR

### Integer XOR

```python
0x41 ^ 0x20
# 97
```

### Byte XOR

```python
bytes([a ^ b for a, b in zip(data, key)])
```

### Single-byte XOR

```python
bytes(c ^ 0x41 for c in data)
```

